{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590080933302272709316.jpeg/2GMXFQF884A9stG3_VqbDQhJST-jRc8o2tmNf_PZjX8\" alt=\"大批警員在場調查。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>大批警員在場調查。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure><p>消息稱，被捕男子姓周（60歲），持有香港身份證，報稱無業。他向銀行櫃檯出示一張寫有要求10萬元的字條，稱自己身上有刀，職員立即按動警鐘，他見狀立即逃走，幸警員及時擒獲，即在其手持的環保袋內，檢獲兩把各長一呎的菜刀及生果刀，其中一把仍有包裝，袋內亦有今日買刀單據。周男涉嫌「企圖行劫」被捕，正被扣查；灣仔警區重案組正調查其行劫原因。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590091071197184870142.jpeg/l2_FjgQ6gHYQMkxmaLtOaUh3qc_wC3lxMf6Zwhj-mcI\" alt=\"警員在涉事恒生銀行調查。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>警員在涉事恒生銀行調查。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590094024118272591684.jpeg/5vvbjBUZ4-fcsAwB8Y8qnQa1J2SwwyUrp8YJlo7GCZY\" alt=\"警員在涉事恒生銀行調查。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>警員在涉事恒生銀行調查。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590082715881472134206.jpeg/Zp3xd0vPJ4gmOXZB4DCI3ZazPoxtg41qrvYMuYf2DLk\" alt=\"疑犯在怡和街與渣甸街交界就擒。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>疑犯在怡和街與渣甸街交界就擒。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590086918705152614320.jpeg/1dvR0zmY9Yl0nHWSaWG0iV19ELW8vSacqXWb74B1m-8\" alt=\"疑犯在怡和街與渣甸街交界就擒。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>疑犯在怡和街與渣甸街交界就擒。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590084087549952258069.jpeg/n0oOnaA8TVl1ia36mW74WgVkYEmQywlUcGld9llpXfY\" alt=\"警員趕抵調查。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>警員趕抵調查。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126590079729405952012493.jpeg/rWcWePbkiXHHDcqM2ZoB_GeJyV1tq53TFwxrYD4Ma2A\" alt=\"警員在涉事恒生銀行調查。（陳浩然攝）\"><figcaption>警員在涉事恒生銀行調查。（陳浩然攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T07:04:05.680020+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":296,"images":7,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}